Privacy Policy for PopupSniper

Last updated: June 29, 2023

This Privacy Policy outlines the privacy practices of PopupSniper (referred to as "we," "us," or "our") in relation to the use of our PopupSniper Chrome Extension.

By using the PopupSniper Chrome Extension, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

1. No Data Collection

PopupSniper does not collect or store any personal data or information from users of our extension. We believe in your right to privacy and, therefore, have built PopupSniper with this fundamental principle in mind. We do not access, gather, or retain any information about your browsing history, personal details, or any other data associated with your usage of the PopupSniper Chrome Extension.

2. Google's Role

As PopupSniper is a Chrome Extension, it operates on the Google Chrome browser. Therefore, any data collected will be through Google's own data collection processes. We have no control over this, and to understand Google's data collection and usage, you should review Google's own privacy policies.

3. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. We encourage users to frequently check this page for any changes. Your continued use of PopupSniper after any change in this Privacy Policy will constitute your acceptance of such change.

By using PopupSniper, you consent to our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our extension. Your continued use of PopupSniper following the posting of changes to our Privacy Policy will be deemed as your acceptance of those changes.

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.
